=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Lucifer-Season-3-DVD/dp/B07DR54BGB/ |website=[[Amazon.co.uk]] |publisher=[[Warner Bros.]] |accessdate=June 17, 2018 |language=English |date=3 September 2018}}</ref>\n| {{n/a|TBA}}\n|}\n\n===Broadcast===\nIn its first three seasons, ''Lucifer'' aired in the United States on [[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]], in [[720p]], [[high-definition television|high definition]], and [[Dolby Digital]] [[5.1 surround sound]]. The first and second seasons aired on Monday at 9 pm ET, before moving to the 8 pm time slot on Monday for the third season. [[Hulu]] owned the exclusive streaming rights in the United States, with each season released after its broadcast on Fox but moved over to Netflix in December 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/news/lucifer-netflix/|title=Lucifer Seasons 1 to 3 Now on Netflix in US and Canada|date=December 15, 2018|website=What's on Netflix}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Albiniak |first1=Paige |title=Hulu Gets Exclusive Rights to 'Blindspot,' 'Lucifer' |url=https://www.broadcastingcable.com/news/hulu-gets-exclusive-rights-blindspot-lucifer-154939 |website=[[Broadcasting & Cable]] |accessdate=June 17, 2018 |language=en-us}}</ref> [[CTV Television Network|CTV]] holds the broadcast rights for Canada.<ref name=\"NW\">{{cite web |title=CTV's Stellar Mid-Season Continues as New Series and Returning Favourites Join the Schedule February and March |url=https://www.newswire.ca/news-releases/ctvs-stellar-mid-season-continues-as-new-series-and-returning-favourites-join-the-schedule-february-and-march-568971991.html |website=[[Newswire]] |accessdate=June 17, 2018 |language=en}}</ref> In the United Kingdom, [[Amazon Video]] holds first-run broadcasting rights, with each episode airing less than 24 hours after the US broadcast.<ref name=\"TVWise\">{{cite web |last1=Munn |first1=Patrick |title=Amazon Prime Instant Video Acquires UK Rights To Fox's 'Lucifer' - TVWise |url=https://www.tvwise.co.uk/2015/10/amazon-prime-instant-video-acquires-uk-rights-to-foxs-lucifer/ |website=TVWise |accessdate=June 17, 2018 |date=26 October 2015}}</ref> It also airs on the television channel [[Fox (UK and Ireland)|FOX]]. The series aired on [[FX (Australian TV channel)|FX]] in Australia<ref name=\"FoxtelUpfronts\">{{cite web|url=http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2015/11/foxtel-upfronts-2016-local-thrillers-lifestyle-us-drama.html|title=Foxtel Upfronts 2016: Local thrillers, Lifestyle & US Drama|last=Knox|first=David|date=November 5, 2015|website=[[TV Tonight]]|accessdate=November 5, 2015}}</ref> before moving to [[FOX8]] during its third season when FX closed<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvtonight.com.au/2018/03/showcase-adds-fx-titles-to-become-super-channel.html|title=Showcase adds FX titles to become \"super channel\"|date=March 1, 2018|work=TV Tonight|first=David|last=Knox}}</ref> and on [[TVNZ1]] in New Zealand.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://independentmedia.net.nz/2015/09/16/tvnz-2016-season-launch-all-you-need-to-know/|title=TVNZ 2016 Season Launch&nbsp;\u2013 All you need to know&nbsp;\u2013 Independent Media New Zealand|access-date=2017-09-05}}</ref>\n\n==Reception==\n\n===Ratings===\n{{Television season ratings\n| hide_18_49_rating = y\n\n| width            = 85\n| link1            = List of Lucifer episodes#Season 1 (2016)\n| timeslot1        = Monday 9:00{{nbsp}}pm\n| timeslot_length1 = 2\n| episodes1        = 13\n| start1           = {{Start date|2016|1|25}}\n| end1             = {{End date|2016|4|25}}\n| startrating1        = 7.16<ref name=\"1.01\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/01/26/monday-final-ratings-scorpion-and-superstore-adjust-up/|title=Monday final ratings: 'Scorpion' and 'Superstore' adjust up|last=Porter|first=Rick|website=TV by the Numbers|date=January 26, 2016|accessdate=January 26, 2016}}</ref>\n| endrating1          = 3.89<ref name=\"1.13\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/04/26/monday-final-ratings-april-25-2016/|title=Monday final ratings: 'The Voice' adjusts down|last=Porter|first=Rick|website=TV by the Numbers|date=April 26, 2016|accessdate=April 26, 2016}}</ref>\n| season1          = 2015\u201316\n| rank1            = 62\n| viewers1         = 7.17<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2016/05/tv-season-2015-2016-series-rankings-shows-full-list-1201763189/|title=Full 2015\u201316 TV Season Series Rankings: 'Blindspot', 'Life In Pieces' & 'Quantico' Lead Newcomers|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Lisa|last=de Moraes|date=May 27, 2016|accessdate=May 27, 2016}}</ref>\n\n| link2            = List of Lucifer episodes#Season 2 (2016\u201317)\n| episodes2        = 18\n| start2           = {{Start date|2016|9|19}}\n| end2             = {{End date|2017|5|29}}\n| startrating2        = 4.36<ref name=\"2.01\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/09/20/monday-final-ratings-sept-19-2016/|title=Monday final ratings: 'Big Bang Theory' and 'Gotham' adjust up, 'Kevin' and 'Good Place' hold|last=Porter|first=Rick|website=TV by the Numbers|date=September 20, 2016|accessdate=September 20, 2016}}</ref>\n| endrating2          = 3.31<ref name=\"2.18\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-may-29-2017/|title='Gotham' adjusts up: Monday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|website=TV by the Numbers|date=May 31, 2017|accessdate=May 31, 2017}}</ref>\n| season2          = 2016\u201317\n| rank2            = 85\n| viewers2         = 5.13<ref name=\"entertainment2017\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/05/2016-2017-tv-season-ratings-series-rankings-list-1202102340/|title=Final 2016-17 TV Rankings: 'Sunday Night Football' Winning Streak Continues|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=May 26, 2017|accessdate=May 26, 2017}}</ref>\n\n| link3            = List of Lucifer episodes#Season 3 (2017\u201318)\n| timeslot3        = Monday 8:00{{nbsp}}pm\n| episodes3        = 26{{efn|name=ThirdSeason26Episodes}}\n| start3           = {{Start date|2017|10|2}}\n| end3         